<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hum, no friend gives that much money to a friend?  =)  Well one of my friends said he'd give me 10kpp to come back to EQ.  After 6 long months of kicking the habit, I couldn't refuse.  He gave me 5kpp and then they nerfed the dwarfs loot.  Needless to say, 5kpp still made me happy and I'm not even so concerned at the other 5kpp he didn't pass onto me.  After all, how many friends do you know that'll let you use their 51 druid when they're not on?  That alone is worth the other 5kpp, especially since I used him to get a GBS!!!<BR>
