<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Suineg</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-24 03:37:25</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Last night a high lev. Troll gave me one of these.  All I had to do was show him the way to Gfay.  I did it with out a thought of a reward, I did it just to try and help out some one who needed it.  I am just a lev. 7 cleric, and I had no idea how much this was worth, and I just found out about this site today.  I just got my EQ accout and am learning how to play.  Now for the point of my post I sold this item for 8pp.  I thought that was a lot and for a lev.7 clerc it is.  But what makes me made is that no one told me what this was worth, no one made any suggestions to what it was worth.  Now i am not trying to complain to much I just wish that some of the other people in the game would be a little more helpful and not just be out for them selves.  I have incountered many very nice people but today all i can think about is how that one person did me wrong, and I know it was my own falt, so I am not blaming anyone I just wish I had this knowlege earlyer today.  To the guy I sold it to enjoy, and to any new people let me give you one pice of advice i learend to "/auctiin" and take some offers before you sell.  Thank you for your time and just try as I do not to do anyone wrong in the game, carma will get you.</font></td></tr></table>
