<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well I wasn't to sure about getting this item for my bard since the AC is so low.  But I figure he will need the extra strength to carry the heavy FS plate and/or Lambent armor someday (he only has 98 strength).<BR>
So putting a bit of extra strength in the non-visable slot made some sense.  Wouldn't pay too much for it though because of the low AC.<BR>
<BR>
And to the last post-- I'm sorry you were "ripped off" on your sale.  But also, you got it for free by doing a good deed.  So anything you got for it is a profit, and you still have the goodwill of the one you helped.<BR>
<BR>
That's why you should always visit this site to take a look at prices first before you sell ;)<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
